## Description ##
Fix the R-package for numpy-compatible shape definition.

@szha @reminisce

1. Fixed a portion of failing tests after introducing numpy compatible shapes.
2. Added a thread-safe switch to turn on/off numpy compatibility. By default, it's off and existing tests should not be affected.

